text: After a second straight week of high unemployment claims and data showing fading job gains, could the labor market be flatlining? @WSJheard looks at the numbers. #WSJWhatsNow https://t.co/B3fWyLbJBS https://t.co/pDatbt4Je6

name: WSJ
text: With pandemic-related job losses still high, some couples are having to adjust to living on one income. We speak to financial planners about the steps households could take to make their finances work in this new reality. https://t.co/jR5UNFjck0
